},{"id":"68e89f982e","type":"paragraph","text":"创办应设评论组。要写一篇文章，写这个问题（指矛盾）。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92e7a727cd","type":"paragraph","text":"《半篮花生》很新鲜，并不难改。里面富裕中农可改为摘帽地主，性质仍是内部矛盾。要把矛盾搞得更激烈些。一家人都有共性，但每个人应有个性。女孩子讲的\"飞跃\"看不出来。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c4a3291d3","type":"paragraph","text":"戏不错，要改好。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0ff4926be6","type":"paragraph","text":"矛盾问题，现在全国都不敢写。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"862ac50fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"《送货路上》：很活泼，内容不错，表演形式有好有坏。拍摄太粗糙。桔子像柿子。台步没有出新。\"莫怕别人指背脊\"，这话不对。演得不错，题材不错。挑杠用的扁担上的双彩球，在《龙江》中已提过，怎么还搞？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5bb986269f","type":"paragraph","text":"《半篮花生》、《送货路上》要改，改完再看。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dee8644d05","type":"paragraph","text":"《两张图纸》：把新干部说得一无是处。当前主席提倡提拔新干部，唱了反调。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ea61d75cb","type":"paragraph","text":"《园丁之歌》：剧名就不合适。园丁应是共产党，怎么是教师、知识分子呢？男教师是二流子。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"508c80b119","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥：教育路线也有问题，学生受教员摆布，女教师是热爱工农的，但最后给小孩子出了难题。）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb1fe70e38","type":"paragraph","text":"教室看不出典型环境。女教师还给男教师说好话，男教师转变也不合理。\"没有文化怎能担起革命重担\"，这句话问题大了，应是\"有文化能更好革命\"。这句话简直是反攻倒算。女的表演简直是青衣花旦，化妆像少奶奶。矛盾也没有很好解决。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bdbdb2f84a","type":"paragraph","text":"音乐创作：","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f155d7d776","type":"paragraph","text":"黄河协奏曲，有人说是俄罗斯作品。今后不要让我们上当了。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7fc911d52","type":"paragraph","text":"《水调歌头》完全可以出新。《浪淘沙》有困难。昆曲太纤细了，非出新不可。刚进城的时候，跟金紫光说过，昆曲可以搞一搞，但他搞的是复古。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"324cf64ee2","type":"paragraph","text":"把《梅花三弄》原曲拿来听一听。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ddc9f18cf8","type":"paragraph","text":"《二泉映月》比较哀怨、压抑。《江河水》比较悲愤，用中西合璧，突出二部。《江河水》要用管子演奏。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"417a2de760","type":"paragraph","text":"《战台风》是个创作，应该提倡。中国音乐是个宝库，应有人搞。要推陈出新，不要搞白手起家。各种地方戏改革动起来了，很可喜，应关心一下。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bac8182d01","type":"paragraph","text":"评剧团的《向阳商店》如何了？据他们说越来越坏了？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba8532cc17","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥：评剧很有观众。）","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e37518822","type":"paragraph","text":"评剧很轻佻，过去家长都不让去看。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec94232984","type":"paragraph","text":"可以调一些戏给我们看，也可以在北京公演。全国创作蓬勃开展，要抓一下评论队伍。创作组要组织一个小的评论组，鼓励创作，指出方向。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c6c220c09","type":"paragraph","text":"（文化部办公厅供稿）","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}},"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0b23939e43","type":"paragraph","text":"《战台风》是个创作，应该提倡。中国音乐是个宝库，应有人搞。要推陈出新，不要搞白手起家。各种地方戏改革动起来了，很可喜，应关心一下。","index":18,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId