的《向阳商店》如何了？据他们说越来越坏了？","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c06522a21c","type":"paragraph","text":"《两张图纸》：把新干部说得一无是处。当前主席提倡提拔新干部，唱了反调。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb63cbd123","type":"paragraph","text":"创办应设评论组。要写一篇文章，写这个问题（指矛盾）。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cbad6bfdbb","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥：教育路线也有问题，学生受教员摆布，女教师是热爱工农的，但最后给小孩子出了难题。）","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d6d70e2a90","type":"paragraph","text":"矛盾问题，现在全国都不敢写。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dcf0433401","type":"paragraph","text":"看到了你们送来的材料了（指创办的\"内刊\"），你们也发现不敢写冲突，写阶级斗争的问题。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df7ddc0a72","type":"paragraph","text":"黄河协奏曲，有人说是俄罗斯作品。今后不要让我们上当了。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f595b3b4d8","type":"paragraph","text":"建议再学习《矛盾论》。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d30df3dc7d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}